# ━━━ Saturn Environment Variables ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Copy this to saturn.env and fill in your values:
#   cp saturn.env.example saturn.env
#
# Saturn is ONE INSTANCE PER REPO — configure the repo it watches below.

# ── LLM / Coding Engine ──
# "cursor"    — delegates ALL coding to Cursor CLI (default)
# "goose"     — delegates coding to Goose CLI (open-source by Block)
# "ollama"    — local LLM agentic loop
# "anthropic" — Anthropic Claude agentic loop
LLM_PROVIDER=goose

# ── Cursor CLI (if LLM_PROVIDER=cursor) ──
# Install: curl https://cursor.com/install -fsS | bash
CURSOR_CLI_PATH=agent
CURSOR_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=600

# ── Goose CLI (if LLM_PROVIDER=goose) ──
# Install: curl -fsSL https://github.com/block/goose/releases/latest/download/goose-installer.sh | bash
GOOSE_CLI_PATH=goose
GOOSE_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=600
# Model provider for Goose (anthropic, openai, ollama, ...)
GOOSE_PROVIDER=anthropic
# Model name (passed to Goose as GOOSE_MODEL env var)
GOOSE_MODEL=claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022

# ── Ollama (legacy — only if LLM_PROVIDER=ollama) ──
OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434
OLLAMA_MODEL=qwen2.5:7b

# ── Anthropic (legacy — only if LLM_PROVIDER=anthropic) ──
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-...

# ── The repo this Saturn instance watches ──
# Saturn maintains a persistent bare clone and uses git worktrees per task.
REPO_URL=https://gitlab.yourcompany.com/group/repo.git
REPO_LOCAL_PATH=/path/to/saturn/repos/myrepo
WORKTREE_BASE_DIR=/path/to/saturn/worktrees

# ── DPAAS Source Tars (provided per branch by CI/CD) ──
# Saturn uses these tars to bootstrap the compilation classpath.
# Paths are relative to the worktree root (or absolute).
DPAAS_SOURCE_TAR=build/ZDPAS/output/dpaas.tar.gz
DPAAS_TEST_TAR=build/ZDPAS/output/dpaas_test.tar.gz

# ── DPAAS Environment ──
# On the runner VM, DPAAS_HOME is set by the shell profile (/opt/dpaas).
# Saturn uses the system DPAAS_HOME if set; falls back to SATURN_DPAAS_HOME.
SATURN_DPAAS_HOME=/data/saturn/dpaas
SATURN_BUILD_FILE_HOME=/home/gitlab-runner/build-files
GITLAB_RUNNER_DPAAS_HOME=/opt/dpaas

# ── Saturn MCP Server (Toolshed — Layer 2) ──
# The Saturn MCP server is registered automatically in Goose's config.
# It provides: compile_quick, run_module_tests, search_code, get_module_context.
# Set to false to disable MCP registration.
MCP_ENABLED=true

# ── GitLab (for MR creation) ──
GITLAB_URL=https://gitlab.yourcompany.com
GITLAB_TOKEN=glpat-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
GITLAB_PROJECT_ID=123
GITLAB_DEFAULT_BRANCH=main

# ── Zoho Cliq (bot posts to channel via zapikey — no OAuth needed) ──
# Get your zapikey from: Cliq Admin → Bots → Your Bot → API → ZAPI Key
CLIQ_BOT_UNIQUE_NAME=saturnbot
CLIQ_BOT_ZAPIKEY=1001.xxxxxxxxxxxx.xxxxxxxxxxxx
CLIQ_BOT_API_URL=https://cliq.zoho.in/api/v2/channelsbyname/yourchannel/message
CLIQ_CHANNEL_UNIQUE_NAME=yourchannel
CLIQ_CHAT_ID=CT_xxxxxxxxxxxx_xxxxxxxxxxxx

# Legacy OAuth (optional — only if zapikey not available)
# CLIQ_AUTH_TOKEN=1000.xxxxxxxxxxxx.xxxxxxxxxxxx

# ── Server ──
SERVER_HOST=0.0.0.0
SERVER_PORT=8000

# ── Agent ──
MAX_LOOP_ITERATIONS=20
THINKING_BUDGET_TOKENS=10000
